+# Base-bundler test fixes test fixes
+
+**Package:** T08
+**Scope:** bundler-packages/base-bundler
+
+## Summary
+Updated stale base-bundler test assertions for the H12 cache fingerprint changes and the current declaration-only DTS output. No scoped source behavior changes were needed. The package test suite is green with the direct package script.
+
+## Tests passing
+all
+
+## Tests still failing
+0
+
+## Changes
+- src/readCache.spec.ts:19 - Updated async read cache expectations to include the optional compile fingerprint argument.
+- src/readCacheSync.spec.ts:19 - Updated sync read cache expectations to include the optional compile fingerprint argument.
+- src/writeCache.spec.ts:55 - Updated async artifact write expectations to include the optional compile fingerprint argument.
+- src/writeCacheSync.spec.ts:52 - Updated sync artifact write expectations to include the optional compile fingerprint argument.
+- src/bundler.spec.ts:515 - Updated DTS declaration assertions for generated contract names.
+- src/bundler.spec.ts:561 - Refreshed async DTS inline snapshot for declaration-only output.
+- src/bundler.spec.ts:657 - Refreshed sync DTS inline snapshot for declaration-only output.
+- src/resolveModuleAsync.spec.ts:327 - Removed a stale one-shot artifact mock and asserted the current undefined-module-path failure behavior.
+- src/resolveModuleSync.spec.ts:318 - Removed a stale one-shot artifact mock and asserted the current undefined-module-path failure behavior.
